<seg id=1> Korean Army Made Accidents in Succession, Opposition Party Challenge Defense Minister Resignation </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> (Reuters, Ltd. Seoul) - Korean opposition party challenged Defense Minister Chun Yong-Taek to resign. Because the army made many accidents before this, including launched missiles and light shell to civilian area. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Korean officials said, the latest accident was a mistake happened in a military operation yesterday morning, the cartridge case of a light shell penetrated two walls of an old woman's home. </seg>
<seg id=4> The old woman's home was close to a place where the missile explosion fragment fell two days ago. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> The Navy officials said, the light shell shot by Korean Marine Corps went farer than expected and dropped at that house in Kimpo. </seg>
<seg id=6> Kimpo is located at the west side of Seoul. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> The opposition party, National People's Party made a statement: "The Defense minister Chun Yong-Taek must resign immediately, otherwise, President Kim Dai-jung must remove him from post. </seg>
<seg id=8> The government that is not afraid of people is not people's government." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=9> The statement said:" Chun Yong-Taek tried to keep his position, he just made an apology......this was false pride." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=10> Ministry of Defense made an apology the day before yesterday for the accident of missile launching. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=11> Navy officials said, the cartridge case of a light shell penetrated two walls of an old woman's house and entered her bath-room. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=12> He said, that 83 years old woman was sent to a nearby hospital due to over frightening. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=13> Last Friday, Korean army accidentally launched a ground to air missile; the missile exploded, caused three civilians injured. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=14> The official of Ministry of National Defense said, when military technical persons in west port city, Inchon, were doing military equipment inspection, this missile was accidentally launched. </seg>
<seg id=15> Inchon is 40 kilometers away from the border between South and North Korea. </seg>
</p>
